ent of orbiting satellites, providing a much-needed\nground-based space radiation analog for future experimentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jun 2017 18:17:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 May 2019 14:45:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-07"}
