ergy. The\ntransition pressures are not found to correlate with $L$. Neutron stars\nobtained with Gogny forces have maximum masses below $1.74M_\\odot$ and\nrelatively small moments of inertia. The crustal mass and moment of inertia are\nevaluated and comparisons are made with the constraints from observed glitches\nin pulsars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jun 2017 19:23:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 01:17:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
