ical solutions that manifest a quasi-periodic character\neven with the strong simplifying assumptions e ~ 0, p = 1, which reduce the\ngoverning equation of J. Wisdom et al. (1984) to a kind of Beletskii equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jun 2017 17:06:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-08"}
